Model:
  z_i ≈ Σ_k Φ_k(t_{ik}) β_k    (Φ_k row-vector b_k, β_k is b_k × p')
  W_i = U_i U_i^T low-rank (rank q << p')
  r_i = z_i - Σ_k Φ_k(t_{ik}) β_k
  F = (1/2) Σ_i ||r_i||²_{W_i} + (1/2) Σ_k tr(β_k^T S_k β_k) + Σ_i P_iso + P_sparse

Sections required:

1. Per-point Hessian block H_{t_i t_i} (d_k × d_k):
   (a) Gauss-Newton: J_k^T β_k W_i β_k^T J_k
   (b) Curvature: -Σ_{a,b} (H^Φ_k)_{ab} β_k W_i r_i
   (c) Isometry-penalty Hessian ∂²P_iso/∂t²
