5. Arrow log-det: log|H| = Σ_i log|H_{t_i t_i}| + log|Schur_β|.

6. Low-rank contraction order (every operation contracts via U_i, never materializes p' × p').

7. Numerical stability (collisions, rank-deficient W, ridge regularization, Woodbury identity).

